props.align: Applies the (align-items)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-items] css property. Available options are **start**, **center**, **end**, **baseline** and **stretch**.
props.alignContent: Applies the (align-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-content] css property. Available options are **start**, **center**, **end**, **space-between**, **space-around** and **stretch**.
props.alignContentLg: Changes the (align-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-content] property on large and greater breakpoints.
props.alignContentMd: Changes the (align-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-content] property on medium and greater breakpoints.
props.alignContentSm: Changes the (align-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-content] property on small and greater breakpoints.
props.alignContentXl: Changes the (align-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-content] property on extra large and greater breakpoints.

props.alignSm: Changes the (align-items)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-items] property on small and greater breakpoints.
props.alignXl: Changes the (align-items)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-items] property on extra large and greater breakpoints.
props.justify: Applies the (justify-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/justify-content] css property. Available options are start, center, end, space-between and space-around.
props.justifyLg: Changes the (justify-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/justify-content] property on large and greater breakpoints.
props.justifyMd: Changes the (justify-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/justify-content] property on medium and greater breakpoints.
props.justifySm: Changes the (justify-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/justify-content] property on small and greater breakpoints.
props.justifyXl: Changes the (justify-content)[https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/justify-content] property on extra large and greater breakpoints.
